webpackJsonp([0x527990c6c3867400],{"./node_modules/json-loader/index.js!./.cache/json/javascript-loops-break-statements.json":function(e,t){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<h2>Introduction</h2>\n<p>The <strong>break</strong> statement terminates the current loop, <code>switch</code> or <code>label</code> statement and transfers program control to the statement following the terminated statement.</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight">\n      <pre class="language-none"><code>break;</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>If the <strong>break</strong> statement is used in a labeled statement, the syntax is as follows:</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight">\n      <pre class="language-none"><code>break labelName;</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p><a href=\'https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/break\' target=\'_blank\' rel=\'nofollow\'>MDN link</a> | <a href=\'https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/3fhdxafb.aspx\' target=\'_blank\' rel=\'nofollow\'>MSDN link</a></p>\n<h2>Examples</h2>\n<p>The following function has a <strong>break</strong> statement that terminates the <code>while</code> loop when <strong>i</strong> is 3, and then returns the value <strong>3 * x</strong>.</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight">\n      <pre class="language-none"><code>function testBreak(x) {\n  var i = 0;\n\n  while (i < 6) {\n    if (i == 3) {\n      break;\n    }\n    i += 1;\n  }\n\n  return i * x;\n}</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p><img src="//forum.freecodecamp.com/images/emoji/emoji_one/rocket.png?v=2" title=":rocket:" alt=":rocket:" class="forum-image"> <a href=\'https://repl.it/C7VM/0\' target=\'_blank\' rel=\'nofollow\'>Run Code</a></p>\n<p>In the following example, the counter is set up to count from 1 to 99; however, the <strong>break</strong> statement terminates the loop after 14 counts.</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight">\n      <pre class="language-none"><code>for (var i = 1; i < 100; i++) {\n  if (i == 15) {\n    break;\n  }\n}</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p><img src="//forum.freecodecamp.com/images/emoji/emoji_one/rocket.png?v=2" title=":rocket:" alt=":rocket:" class="forum-image"> <a href=\'https://repl.it/C7VO/0\' target=\'_blank\' rel=\'nofollow\'>Run Code</a></p>',fields:{slug:"/javascript/loops/break-statements/"},frontmatter:{title:"Break Statement"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/javascript/loops/break-statements/"}}}});
